{"tid":2375341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"消息：政府擬周末期間於佐敦實施禁足令強制檢測","createTime":"2021-01-22T03:12:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T18:41:31.000Z","uid":13663,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d920c7cbdd4c137d20f12362fd581b48216b6dcc","tid":2375341,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T03:12:44.000Z","msg":"消息指，政府正考慮可能在星期六、日期間，在早前收緊強制檢測門檻的「佐敦指定區域」部分範圍，實施「禁足令」強制檢測，但未有定案，如果實行，政府會調動大批紀律部隊人員及檢測人員參與。 政府上月修訂香港法例第599J章規例，容許食物及衞生局局長將指定地點列為「受限處所」，在限制與檢測宣告發出後，範圍內人士必須留下，直至所有有關人士完成檢測，而有關檢測結果獲確定方可離開，條文亦為離開有關受限處所提供合理辯解，例如需接受緊急診治。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2375840\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2375840&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4TdagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=74ae7a64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2375840</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5b88bc4277605c99c99342c72bbede397929af0","tid":2375341,"uid":303805,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T03:13:55.000Z","msg":"同班狗r ot"},{"pid":"cbfea71153afbd14d721c92a39fcdb070016e1cd","tid":2375341,"uid":82640,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T03:14:35.000Z","msg":"支那小區封個屋苑<br />\n香港成區講緊要封幾十個屋苑<br />\n舊區更加無邊無際可言<br />\n聽支那佬老點嘅港府等出事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab014eb073ca1b87273ae221ea73f6b3024e4f03","tid":2375341,"uid":77196,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d5b88bc4277605c99c99342c72bbede397929af0","tid":2375341,"uid":303805,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T03:13:55.000Z","msg":"同班狗r ot"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T03:14:36.000Z","msg":"班狗怕死多過想要OT錢"},{"pid":"7832b91e1bc62c1abd277ef8168ef124c15dea17","tid":2375341,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T03:15:19.000Z","msg":"召喚返工四人幫"},{"pid